              <div class="node node-story node-promoted node-sticky node-teaser clearfix" id="node-10002">
               <h2>
                <a href="/node/10002">
                 New 2018 HIRO Fee Schedule Released
                </a>
               </h2>
               <div class="content">
                <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
                 <div class="field-items">
                  <div class="field-item even">
                   <p>
                    The HIRO's fee schedule and related policies were updated and circulated on May 8, 2018. The new fee schedule takes effect on July 1, 2018. The full fee schedule and related memos can be reviewed
                    <a href="/fees">
                     on the Fees page of our website
                    </a>
                    . If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the HIRO.
                   </p>
                  </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <ul class="links inline">
